name: Lumberjack Notebook
description:
These journals / notebooks are A6 (148mm x 105mm) and made from acid free brown kraft paper. The journals are machine made with a glued spine. The paper is 90gsm and each journal had 120 sheets.

The images used are from vintage childrens books that were being thrown away because they were too damaged for sale.
